Q1. Write a Python program to list all files and folders in the current directory using os.listdir(). 

import os
items = os.listdir()
print("Files and Folders in current directory:")
for item in items:
    print(item)


Q2. Build a package education with a sub package courses, containing modules science.py and  arts.py. Each module should have a function get_subjects(). Write a python program to display all  subjects.    

def science_get_subjects():
    return ["Physics", "Chemistry", "Biology"]
def arts_get_subjects():
    return ["History", "Geography", "Literature"]
print("Science Subjects:")
for sub in science_get_subjects():
    print(sub)
print("\nArts Subjects:")
for sub in arts_get_subjects():
